• *Sketches and Stories* (Очерки и рассказы), 1899, a collection that marked the beginning of his widespread fame.

• *[Makar Chudra](/Makar_Chudra)* (Макар Чудра), 1892, his debut published short story.

• *[Old Izergil](/Old_Izergil)* (Старуха Изергиль), 1895, a collection of tales exploring human nature and freedom.

• *[Chelkash](/Chelkash)* (Челкаш), 1895, a powerful story of a tramp and a peasant.

