• *Varenka Olesova* (Варенька Олесова), 1898.

• *[Twenty-six Men and a Girl](/Twenty-six_Men_and_a_Girl)* (Двадцать шесть и одна), 1899, a poignant tale of resilience and vulnerability.

### Plays

• *[The Philistines](/The_Philistines)* (Мещане), translated also as *The Smug Citizens* and *The Petty Bourgeois* (Мещане), 1901, a critique of the stagnant middle class.

